Okay, let's build a complete Flask web application with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This example will create a simple to-do list application.  It will allow users to add, delete, and mark tasks as complete.

**Core Files and Structure**

First, let's outline the project structure:

```
my_todo_app/
â”œâ”€â”€ app.py         # Flask application logic
â”œâ”€â”€ templates/
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ index.html   # HTML template
â”œâ”€â”€ static/
